Language: <F P=105> Pashto </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Esteemed Professor Borhanoddin Rabbani, president of 
the Islamic State of Afghanistan, has sent to Tashkent a message 
of gratitude addressed to Islam Karimov, president of 
Uzbekistan, in response to the latter's message of 
congratulation on the occasion of the month of Ramadan. 
  The message says: I express gratitude for your message of 
congratulation addressed to me on the arrival of the blessed 
month of Ramadan. On my behalf I congratulate you on the month 
of Ramadan and all Muslim people of that republic. I hope that 
the Muslim people of the Republic of Uzbekistan pass these 
auspicious days in tranquility. I wish from God prosperity for 
you and the people of Uzbekistan. 

